---
title: Teriyaki- Glazed Meatballs with Crunchy Cabbage Slaw and Basmati Rice
description: We’re giving meatballs an Asian twist with homemade teriyaki sauce. Made with soy, ginger, and a touch of honey for sweetness, it’s a major upgrade from the bottle. We’re serving this delicious dish over rice and adding a refreshing cabbage slaw for crunch!
